CustomField.description: From Annual Survey: If member entered a range (ex 25-100), then data here is the average of that range. (This may not meet the criteria for the benchmark which must be 50 diapers per child per month for 90% of all routine distributions.)
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The average number of diapers distributed per child monthly. Note: The criteria to meet this benchmark is 50 diapers per child per month for at least 90% of all routine distributions.
CustomField.label: Diapers Per Child Monthly
